OL,7,FA boy from Kent who was born with
OL,8,Fserious health conditions affecting
OL,9,Fhis sight, hearing and mobility, has
OL,10,Fdefied the odds and taken his very
OL,11,Ffirst steps.
OL,13,FDoctors told Malachi Martin's parents
OL,14,Fthat he would never be able to walk or
OL,15,Ftalk.
OL,17,FBut, remarkably, Malachi, 11, from
OL,18,FTunbridge Wells has been able to take
OL,19,Fhis first steps, thanks to a special
OL,20,Fimmersive experience room at Chailey
OL,21,FHeritage School in Sussex.
