OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Malachi's
OL,8,Fmother Claire said: "As soon as he was
OL,9,Fborn, it was obvious there was things
OL,10,Fwrong, so it was quite traumatic.
OL,12,F"The doctor basically said that he
OL,13,Fprobably would never walk, talk, eat,
OL,14,For too much, really."
OL,16,FMalachi's father Brendan said they
OL,17,Fgrieve for what he loses in life.
OL,19,F"It takes a long time to realise
OL,20,Factually you've had the most
OL,21,Fbeautiful, wonderful child," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
