OL,3,CBoy who was told he would never walk
OL,4,Ctakes first steps thanks to sensory
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,F"He has a beautiful life."
OL,9,FBut now Malachi is taking his first
OL,10,Ftentative steps towards a brighter
OL,11,Ffuture - stimulated by the sights and
OL,12,Fsounds of a special immersive space at
OL,13,FChailey Heritage School in East Sussex.
OL,15,F"Just seeing your child able to do so
OL,16,Fmany things that you thought he
OL,17,Fwouldn't be able to, but actually
OL,18,Fyou've hoped he could, you've given
OL,19,Fhim those opportunities," Claire added.
