OL,7,FMichelle Maskell class teacher at
OL,8,FChailey School said: "When we took
OL,9,FMalachi to the immersive space, he was
OL,10,Fjust so excited by all of the images
OL,11,Fon the screen, so we started taking
OL,12,Fhis walker in with us.
OL,14,F"We had fireworks displayed on the
OL,15,Fprojection, it was really good for
OL,16,FMalachi's vision, and also it had the
OL,17,Fbang sound, which again is good for
OL,18,FMalachi to hear, because he really
OL,19,Fresponds to things that light up and
OL,20,Fthings that make a sound.
