OL,7,F"The combination of the two for him
OL,8,Fwere really exciting, and then he
OL,9,Fgradually started to try to step, and
OL,10,Fover the weeks, he stepped more and
OL,11,Fmore until he touched the actual image.
OL,13,F"We were so excited as a team, we were
OL,14,Fin tears.
OL,16,F"We praised him and encouraged him,
OL,17,Fand he got there, and it was
OL,18,Ffantastic."
